If you can’t get away from your desk for lunch, stay in your chair and chew on a list of quirky YouTube channels. The List ’s Holly Morgan shows us a few that will that will give you a break from work, entertain and educate on What’s Trending . What To Watch On Your Lunch Break 

Comedian Paul Gale does quick sketches on everyday blunders you can relate to. The Odd Chick 
Ask A Mortician , Caitlin Doughty, answers questions about death that make this natural process less frightening. The Brainiac 
Physics Girl makes learning fun by using everyday objects to explain complex ideas. The Nutrition Nerds 
The Food Heaven Show stars a couple of dieticians who want you to eat better.
